===Noun===
{{en-noun|match|matches}}

#<!--DefA-->Device made of wood or paper, coated with chemicals at the tip, that when dragged against a rough surface, will catch fire.
#<!--DefB-->Sporting event such as a boxing meet, a baseball game, or a cricket match
#<!--DefC-->Someone as skillful as self. ''He knew he had met his '''match'''.'' 

